{"tid":1414601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人仲需要時間","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:41.000Z","uid":60592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d62412cbe8195cad41bff95aa2340e186883355","tid":1414601,"uid":60592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"發夢今日係我第一次上前線<br />\n<br />\n發現到嘅野就係無論有幾多黑衣人，附近總係有好多遊離派根本唔會體諒/開始接受唔到更多或更大力度嘅行為，就算你擺個問題係政府/狗到佢都會覺得你搵緊藉口。因為佢地自細就覺得對抗政府係一件好難好遙遠嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地接收資訊係隔左好多層，佢地個心根本無果種真係好撚唔忿氣同有真正想改變呢個心態，更多當然係唔知點做嘅心態。<br />\n<br />\n但係，香港其實呢啲人係佔好多數，而建立一個新社會/推翻政權正正就係需要容納同埋改變呢堆人，所以長期嘅同更大嘅文宣/教育係而家最重要，特別係遊行已經去多一個樽勁位。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論。"},{"pid":"e2421a4127d269f61fc97bcf14de1bee37f53d2d","tid":1414601,"uid":60592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3491a45b74430653f051778472a621f00a3be8c","tid":1414601,"uid":60592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e1b2c0c50331594fe90a4fcd1230859fee935e","tid":1414601,"uid":60592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eb7c287c078a75f0c92626c758fc9409a0e11b","tid":1414601,"uid":60592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a